<div class="text-white text-center">
    <p class="display-4 fs-1 mb-0 lh-1">WELCOME TO OUR</p>
    <h1 class="mb-4 lh-1" style="font-size: 5rem; font-weight: bold;">RULES AND REGULATIONS</h1>
