<!-- About the Rules and Regulations -->
<section class="bg-light py-5">
    <div class="container text-center">
        <h2 class="display-5 mb-4">Community Guidelines</h2>
        <p class="lead">
            Our community thrives on respect, security, and cooperation. These rules and regulations ensure a peaceful and well-maintained environment for all residents. By following them, we create a harmonious space where everyone can live comfortably and safely.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Code of Conduct Section -->
<section class="bg-white py-5">
    <div class="container text-center">
        <h2 class="display-5 mb-4">Code of Conduct</h2>
        <p class="lead">
            Every resident plays a role in upholding the integrity of our community. Respecting neighbors, maintaining cleanliness, and observing noise regulations contribute to a better living experience for all. Let’s practice courtesy and consideration every day.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Safety and Security Section -->
<section class="bg-primary text-white py-5">
    <div class="container text-center">
        <h2 class="display-5 mb-4">Safety & Security</h2>
        <p class="lead">
            The safety of our residents is our top priority. Adhering to community security measures, reporting suspicious activities, and following emergency procedures help ensure a secure environment where everyone can feel at ease.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Community Responsibilities Section -->
<section class="bg-light py-5">
    <div class="container text-center">
        <h2 class="display-5 mb-4">Resident Responsibilities</h2>
        <p class="lead">
            Being a responsible resident means taking care of shared spaces, following waste disposal guidelines, and participating in community initiatives. By doing our part, we foster a cleaner, more organized, and more welcoming neighborhood.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>

